Video Summary: Connect Gmail to n8n in 4 Minutes (2025)
By Palmer Joseph – Quick tutorial on integrating n8n with Gmail for email automation (e.g., managing clients/deadlines).
Key Steps:

Install n8n & add Gmail trigger (on new message).
Set up Google Cloud project/OAuth consent (external, add test user).
Create OAuth client (web app), add n8n callback URI, copy ID/secret.
Paste into n8n credentials, authorize via Google sign-in.
Enable Gmail API in Google Cloud.

Message: Enables AI-powered Gmail automations like auto-responses/pulling emails—game-changer for workflows. (92 words)


